Request -> Create Request 

First and last names should only contain alphabets.

Phone numbers should be displayed according to the country code.
 
For round trip bookings, if the date is in the past, an error message should indicate the issue.


SR Flight Request

Updating a 'One Way' flight to 'Multi City' doesn't show the option to add cities or countries.

Round-trip bookings should only allow present and future dates, but past dates are currently allowed.

SR Hospital Request

Hospital booking dates should only allow present and future dates, but past dates are currently allowed.

